    oc:appliesToContext "When conducting technical SEO audits" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Core Web Vitals thresholds must be met: LCP <2.5s, FID <100ms, CLS <0.1. Common fixes include image optimization, lazy loading, minifying CSS/JS, CDN implementation, and deferring non-critical JS." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Core Web Vitals are a Google ranking factor and directly impact user experience and bounce rates." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

