    oc:appliesToContext "When validating content SEO readiness before and after publishing" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Before publishing checklist: primary keyword in title, keyword in first 100 words, H2/H3 include keywords naturally, alt text on images, 3-5 internal links, 2-3 external authority links, optimized meta description, clean keyword URL, content exceeds competitors. After: submit to GSC, share socially, build internal links, monitor rankings." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Comprehensive checklist ensures no optimization opportunity is missed and provides a measurable quality gate." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

